'''Pip''' was a globe-headed arachnid-like systems control [[Droid/Legends|droid]] propelled by a set of telescoping legs. It was stationed on [[Ruan]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. The droid helped [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] locate [[Droma]], after the [[Ryn/Legends|Ryn]] was arrested for conspiracy for forging documents.<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos II: Jedi Eclipse">''[[The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos II: Jedi Eclipse]]''</ref>

